Sentece: After intracameral administration (4.5 μg) of solubilized brinzolamide, aqueous humor concentrations were described with a two-compartment model, the estimated clearance was 4.12 μL/min, apparent volume of distribution at steady-state 673 μL, and terminal half-life 3.4 h.
Title: Comprehensive Ocular and Systemic Pharmacokinetics of Brinzolamide in Rabbits After Intracameral, Topical, and Intravenous Administration.
